preview_text:
Hey Kevin, let me be the first to welcome you to MeetMindful! You've already set up your account and found your way to your inbox, which is great. Also, we've just added two free days of MeetMindful Premium to your account, so you can send and receive messages (like this one) for free until Saturday at 11:59pm PDT.

After the two days with Premium are up, you owe us nothing :) You can still browse your matches and "Like" them to let them know you're interested, and we'll keep sending you matches via Email as well, but you'll need a Premium membership in order to keep your conversations going. For the best chance of early success, I'd recommend filling out the rest of your profile before you reach out to anyone. This is what people come here for! I can tell you, your matches are far more likely to respond that way.

Thanks again for joining us, and I think you'll love the community we're building here. We want you to enjoy your time using MeetMindful so let us know how we can help with that anytime, and have fun!

Adam
Co-Founder, MeetMindful

P.S. If you have any questions for us you can check out our thorough Help Center at Settings > Help Center.
